nTitle: This week in Nushell #222
Path: Nushell
Content:
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11057] made it possible to pass switch values dynamically
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10851] improved redirection so it supports redirecting stderr while piping stdout to the next command
ysthakur created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11006] a spread operator for list literals
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11097] deprecated 
``std clip``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10999] removed 
``def-env``
 and 
``export def-env``
hustcer made lots of fixes to the release workflows: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11146] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11145] 2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11121] 3
drbrain did several internal refactorings to help with error messages (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11126] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11125] 2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11124] 3
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11123] 4
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11120] 5
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11119] 6
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11118] 7
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11094] 8
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11093] 9
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10983] 10
) and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10970] added a new 
``is-terminal``
 command to determine if stdin/out/err are a terminal
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11122] moved more commands to the opaque 
``Record``
 type
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11115] bumped 
``procfs``
 to 0.16.0
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11114] bumped the Nu version to 
``0.87.2``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11075] used the new record API in 
``describe --detailed``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11052] improved developer documentation
danielsomerfield 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11112] fixed the toolkit to run for the whole workspace on 'check pr'
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11066] refactored 
``Value``
 cell path functions to fix bugs
tskinn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11005] added a new 
``mktemp``
 command
MarikaChlebowska 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10962] added a more descriptive error message when passing a list to 
``from_csv``
