sholderbach created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1153] Clean up contributor book
ppenguin created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1152] Add 
``parse``
 examples to 
Parsing
arnau created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1151] Unifies all cookbook codeblocks to use the same style.
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1150] Add a cookbook comparing jq and nushell
132ikl created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1142] Add a snippet to suggest using the ? operator for environmental variables
íŸ@2503291d7537b6993a157e9a2c0f7a787b4d610258e4cdbea5dd8ea93e3db047⁄ñTitle: This week in Nushell #222
Path: Nu_Scripts
Content:
amtoine created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/674] add 
``clip``
 from standard library
WindSoilder created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/673] Using def --env instead of def-env
fj0r created 
